1055
00:58:44,102 --> 00:58:49,656
Ten, nine, eight,
seven, six,

1056
00:58:49,724 --> 00:58:55,695
five, four, three,
two, one...

1057
00:59:00,335 --> 00:59:02,119
You know, all you young
people who are applauding,

1058
00:59:02,187 --> 00:59:03,938
you should go
fuck yourselves.

1059
