1115
01:03:29,570 --> 01:03:31,221
I'm great. I'm great.

1116
01:03:31,289 --> 01:03:33,840
You remember?
We were in the hospital together, right?

1117
01:03:33,908 --> 01:03:36,460
We were...
Were you at Milestones?

1118
01:03:36,528 --> 01:03:37,994
No. I didn't go to Milestones.

1119
