and help turn my life around.

1150
01:05:13,774 --> 01:05:14,958
Listen, I'm in
a great group.

1151
01:05:15,025 --> 01:05:16,626
Rachel. I...

1152
01:05:16,694 --> 01:05:19,262
I'm so glad to hear it. Excuse me.
Sir, just stop.

1153
01:05:19,330 --> 01:05:22,215
Sorry, I just need
