made our childhood a living hell

1162
01:05:44,905 --> 01:05:48,175
and explains away all your
shit in one fell swoop.

1163
01:05:48,242 --> 01:05:49,826
Did you tell them
that Dad forced us

1164
01:05:49,894 --> 01:05:51,811
