hate the lies.

1173
01:06:29,217 --> 01:06:31,201
I mean,
she lied in rehab.

1174
01:06:31,269 --> 01:06:32,819
What do you mean,
she lied?

1175
01:06:32,886 --> 01:06:34,871
I mean, she lied to the people
who were working with her,

1176
01:06:34,939 --> 01:06:37,273
